<reference id="cmd" xml:lang="en-us">
   <title>
      <keyword>cmd</keyword>
   </title>
   <shortdesc>The command (&lt;<keyword>cmd</keyword>&gt;) element is required as the first element
inside a &lt;<keyword>step</keyword>&gt;. It provides the active voice instruction to the
user for completing the step, and should not be more than one sentence. If
the step needs additional explanation, this can follow the &lt;<keyword>cmd</keyword>&gt; element
inside an <ph>
         <xref href="info.xml">info</xref>
      </ph> element.</shortdesc>
